{"tid":1071575,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"至少6死30重傷】江蘇化工廠大爆炸 波及1km外幼園多名兒童傷","createTime":"2019-03-21T12:28:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-21T12:28:10.000Z","uid":47359,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f04f29e9567d9b5660ff861519d788311788fb3d","tid":1071575,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T12:28:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190321/59394517\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190321%2F59394517&d=tFviIiuTv25K9aUiQ%2BXN3G8KfKULefuOMk0AcQ9dAAw%3D&h=3d3cc1af\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190321%2F59394517&h=2e170ac3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190321/59394517</a><br />\n<br />\n（新增：內容及動新聞）江蘇鹽城化工廠於今日下午2時許發生爆炸，現場火光沖天，冒出蘑菇雲。截至下午7時，事故造成6人死亡、30人重傷，另有部份民眾不同程度輕傷。中國地震局通報指，今日下午2時48分在江蘇連雲港市灌南縣疑似爆炸，錄得2.2級地震，震源深度0公里。下午5時許，鹽城市響水縣委宣傳發佈《響水天嘉宜化工爆炸情況匯報》，內容指今日下午2時48分左右，位於響水縣生態化工園區的天嘉宜化工有限公司發生爆炸。通報迴避傷亡情況。"}]}